properties.value: Assess results of additional or own research
Kennisnemen van de resultaten van aanvullend onderzoek of door de arts zelf uitgevoerd onderzoek en deze betrekken bij diagnose en behandelplan.
Taking note of the results of additional diagnostic tests or results of the examinations carried out by care provider himself and including these in the diagnosis and treatment plan.
